snippet.title: How to Train Your Gavin
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Gavin, just trying to make it in this big ol' booktuber world. I've had this channel since 2006 and I've uploaded fan videos of some of my favourite things (especially Disney-related stuff), but now I'm hoping to keep it simple with some booktube videos! Please do subscribe and chat to me about everything and anything. 

I'm also a writer on Wattpad, I wrote a Watty Award winning book called "Heart of the Sky" which is a Gay Titanic present-day retelling set on a luxury airplane instead of a ship. I'm so proud of it, I love it to bits, and if you want to check out some of my other works, then please do.

I also work as an ambassador for Reach Out Volunteers and as a Children's and YA bookseller.

You can support me and my channel by joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/GavinHetherington
